'''Ururka Oromo Peoples Democraticka'''


{{Flag|Ethiopia}}



Ururka Dimoqraadiga ee Oromo (OPDO) waa xisbiga siyaasadeed ee Itoobiya, qayb ka mid ah isbahaysiga Dhaqdhaqaaqa Dimuqraadiyadda Qaranka ee Amhara, Jabhadda Dimuqraadiyadda ee Koonfurta Itoobiya iyo Jabhadda Tigreega Jabhadaha Tigreega ee ka kooban Jabhadda Dib-u-kicinta Dimuqraadiyada ee Itoobiya (EPRDF). Doorashadii ugu danbaysay ee sharci-dejinta, 15-kii Maajo 2005, xisbigu wuxuu qayb ka ahaa Jabhadda Dib-u-kicinta Dimuqraadiga Dadweynaha, oo ku guuleystay 327 527 kursi. [2]
Doorashadii Golaha Wakiilada ee August 2005, xisbigu wuxuu ku guuleystay 387 kursi 537 kursi oo ku yaal gobolka Oromia, iyo 14 ka mid ah 36 kursi oo ka tirsan Gobolka Harari.














